# Ravioli, Ravioli

A funny PC game about hitting clients in an italian restaurant.

## Gameplay

Serve customers quickly while maintaining quality in a chaotic kitchen environment. Balance speed with customer satisfaction!

### Game Mechanics

- Time management challenges
- Customer satisfaction system
- Upgrade your kitchen equipment
- Unlock new recipes

## Technologies

- Unity Engine for game development
- C# Programming for game logic
- Custom AI System for customer behavior
- Hand-drawn art style

## Story

You play as a chef in a bustling Italian restaurant where things don't always go according to plan. Keep your customers happy (or hit them with ravioli when they're too demanding)!

## Awards

- Best Humor in Gaming 2024
- Indie Game Festival Finalist
